description:
MyUnitel is the Unitel application that allows you to manage your account.

Register and take advantage of all the features we make available to you.

- Simplified and faster registration and login;
- Greater security and protection of customer data through the use of biometric authentication and OTP;
- Greater comfort in the user experience, through an interface designed to meet the customer's needs;
- Greater ease and more fluidity in the management of Unitel services, plans, tariffs and payments;
- Ease of viewing charging events and consumption of voice, data and SMS balances;
- Ease of interaction with different customer support channels through a dedicated area;
- Quick and easy access to information about Unitel services, plans and stores without having to leave the App;
- Comprehensive management of the NET CASA 4G and 5G offer;
- Greater integration with the native functionalities of iOS and Android operating systems (For example: Phonebook);
- More modern image/interface and fully adjusted to the Unitel brand.
